WEBVTT

00:01.379 --> 00:02.711
<i>Before there was sex...</i>

00:02.714 --> 00:05.096
<i>Before there was the city,</i>
<i>there was just me,</i>

00:05.216 --> 00:07.950
<i>Carrie... Carrie Bradshaw</i>
<i>from Castlebury, Connecticut.</i>

00:07.952 --> 00:09.051
I love you.

00:09.053 --> 00:11.387
There are so many soirees
now in the city.

00:11.389 --> 00:12.688
- I know.
- Do you?

00:12.690 --> 00:15.023
How's my article coming?

00:15.025 --> 00:18.026
Actually, I decided
not to finish the piece.

00:18.028 --> 00:19.294
You know what?
I just don't think

00:19.296 --> 00:20.529
it's gonna happen for you
right now,

00:20.531 --> 00:22.130
but be a love
and go make me a cappuccino.

00:22.132 --> 00:24.066
I'm pregnant.
Maggie, I'm engaged.

00:24.068 --> 00:25.300
What am I gonna do?

00:25.302 --> 00:26.969
We'll figure out what
your choices are... together.

00:26.971 --> 00:29.504
It appears your daughter
has an ectopic pregnancy.

00:29.506 --> 00:31.373
You are a lowlife,
getting my daughter pregnant,

00:31.375 --> 00:33.809
- putting her life at risk.
- Why didn't you tell Maggie's parents

00:33.811 --> 00:35.077
that you're not the father?

00:35.079 --> 00:36.878
She wouldn't want her parents,
especially her dad

00:36.880 --> 00:38.513
to know she was involved
with Simon.

00:38.515 --> 00:40.482
Do you not understand
what people will think of you?

00:40.484 --> 00:43.051
The only thing I care about
is that you know the truth.

00:43.171 --> 00:46.903
