00:52.328 --> 00:55.730
<i>The holiday season</i>
<i>is a time to be grateful...</i>

00:55.732 --> 00:59.000
♪ I was feeling cold and tired

00:59.002 --> 01:00.268
<i>to give thanks...</i>

01:00.270 --> 01:03.104
♪ Yeah,
kinda sad and uninspired ♪

01:03.106 --> 01:06.174
<i>and this year,</i>
<i>I was thankful for so much.</i>

01:06.176 --> 01:08.009
I'm so lucky.

01:08.011 --> 01:09.144
I love you.

01:09.146 --> 01:11.446
<i>It was a time</i>
<i>for second chances.</i>

01:11.448 --> 01:14.249
♪ The Grace and feel the magic
in your touch ♪

01:14.251 --> 01:16.359
♪ oh, lay your hands

01:18.321 --> 01:19.954
♪ Lay your hands on me

01:19.956 --> 01:21.756
♪ lay your hands

01:21.758 --> 01:24.159
♪ ooh, ooh, ooh

01:24.161 --> 01:25.627
♪ lay your hands

01:25.629 --> 01:29.430
<i>but not everyone in Castlebury</i>
<i>was in the holiday spirit.</i>

01:29.432 --> 01:31.065
I knew this was a bad idea.

01:31.067 --> 01:32.734
I shouldn't have
come back to school.

01:32.736 --> 01:36.237
- Should've just told everyone I was sick...
- forever.

01:36.689 --> 01:38.923
You have
nothing to be ashamed of.

01:38.925 --> 01:41.225
You were out
with a burst appendix.

01:41.227 --> 01:43.260
At least that's
what I've been telling everyone.

01:43.262 --> 01:44.662
Thanks, Carrie.
But you know,

01:44.664 --> 01:46.564
half the town
knows that I was pregnant,

01:46.566 --> 01:48.432
and the other half thinks
that I was out

01:48.434 --> 01:50.668
because you beat me up
to get your boyfriend back.

01:50.670 --> 01:52.470
People just love a juicy story
so they don't have to think

01:52.472 --> 01:53.904
about their own boring lives.

01:53.906 --> 01:55.739
They'll forget about it
in a week

01:55.741 --> 01:57.508
when something else comes up.

01:57.510 --> 01:59.343
I don't know. I have
a terrible poker face.

01:59.345 --> 02:01.078
It's gonna be hard to hide
that this is

02:01.080 --> 02:02.780
one of <i>the</i> worst of my life.

02:02.782 --> 02:06.083
Whoo-hoo! Harvard!
I just got in!

02:06.085 --> 02:10.253
Early admissions. This is
the greatest day of my life.

02:10.256 --> 02:13.223
Yeah, I kick ass.

02:13.225 --> 02:16.193
Um, did you guys just hear me?

02:16.195 --> 02:19.630
I got into Harvard...
in Cambridge?

02:19.632 --> 02:21.432
- Congrats, Mouse.
- That's great, Mouse.

02:21.434 --> 02:22.599
Great.

02:22.601 --> 02:25.369
That's better.
Except Walt's not here.

02:25.371 --> 02:27.404
Way to ruin a perfect moment.

02:27.406 --> 02:29.573
Where the hell is he, anyway?

02:34.512 --> 02:37.314
What's going on?

02:39.183 --> 02:41.251
I've packed some things
for you.

02:43.788 --> 02:46.256
You told dad.

02:46.258 --> 02:48.091
It's something
he should know...

02:48.093 --> 02:49.626
about his son.

02:51.529 --> 02:52.729
Where is he?

02:52.731 --> 02:55.298
He doesn't want to see you.

02:57.935 --> 03:01.505
Can... we please
talk about this?

03:01.507 --> 03:05.342
Do you have any idea
what you've put us through?

03:05.344 --> 03:12.148
Don't make this any harder
than it already is, Walter.

